# Created by Tianyi Zeng 2012 for Artificial Intelligence
# Project: Classification for numbers in images for text extracting from image sources, and face images for face recognition
# Train the classifier on a set of handwritten digit images, then test it with another set of images. Same for human faces.
# My algorithms in: answers.py, naiveBayes.py, perceptron.py
# Algorithms used and compared: Naive Bayes, Perceptron
# How to run
python dataClassifier.py -c naiveBayes --autotune
python dataClassifier.py -c naiveBayes –k 2
python dataClassifier.py -c naiveBayes --autotune –d faces
python dataClassifier.py -a -d digits -c naiveBayes -o -1 3 -2 6
python dataClassifier.py -c perceptron
python dataClassifier.py -c perceptron –w
